{
  "texts": [
    "4.4.2 Infrastructure Scanning.",
    "In DevSecOps, Infrastructure Scanning plays a crucial role in ensuring the security and compliance of software systems.",
    "With the rise of Infrastructure as Code (IaC) tools like Ansible, Chef, and Puppet, the process of provisioning and configuring infrastructure has become more automated and scalable.",
    "These tools allow developers and operations teams to define infrastructure configurations as machine-readable code, enabling consistent, repeatable deployments across environments.",
    "Thus, IaC is a key DevOps practice and a component of continuous delivery [147]."
  ]
}